snippet.title: Hunter Hunted gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Hunter Hunted, PC game produced by Sierra in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/hunter-hunted/2273/
Playing the first few stages of this platform game featuring both the hunter and the hunted beast.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Iron Blood - https://youtu.be/gm-spPIfhHk
Judge Dredd - https://youtu.be/eO2sPSY6_uc
Eracha - https://youtu.be/VTg1By3RKjU
